sql_statement.static: SELECT * FROM vsw_flow_cfg

SELECT FrameSize, Load, OfferedRate, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime))*(SELECT DISTINCT (FixedLoad/MbpsLoad) FROM GeneratorConfig), 0.0) AS ThroughputPercent, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputMbps, COALESCE(((1e6 * Rx.SigFrameCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputFps, COALESCE(Rx.TotalLatency, 0) AS TotalLatency, Rx.AvgLatency AS AvgLatency, Rx.MinLatency AS MinLatency, Rx.MaxLatency AS MaxLatency, COALESCE(Rx.TotalJitter, 0) AS TotalJitter, Rx.AvgJitter AS AvgJitter, Rx.MinJitter AS MinJitter, Rx.MaxJitter AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.FrameCount, 0) AS RxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DroppedFrameCount, TxFrameCount, 0) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * Rx.DroppedFrameCount/TxFrameCount, 100.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, COALESCE(Rx.OutSeqFrameCount, 0) AS OutSeqFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DuplicateFrameCount, 0) AS DuplicateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.LateFrameCount, 0) AS LateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.L1BitCount, 0) AS BitCount, COALESCE(Rx.FirstArrivalTime, 0) AS FirstTime, COALESCE(Rx.LastArrivalTime, 0) AS LastTime, SbTx.ParentHnd AS ParentHnd, TxPort, COALESCE(Rx.PortName, 'NA') AS RxPort, LossTolerance

FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, CASE WHEN Sb.FrameLengthMode='IMIX' THEN 'imix' ELSE Sb.FixedFrameLength END AS FrameSize, (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS Load, (Tx.L1BitCount / ((SELECT DISTINCT Duration FROM GeneratorConfig) * 1e6)) * (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad/MbpsLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS OfferedRate, (SELECT LossTolerance FROM vsw_flow_cfg_iter) AS LossTolerance, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Tx.PortName, 'NA') AS TxPort, Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd FROM Streamblock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Rx.Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort) WHERE SbActive

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_flow_iter_agg (FrameSize INTEGER, FlowCount INTEGER, Load FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps INTEGER, MinThroughputPercent FLOAT, MaxThroughputPercent FLOAT, TotalLatency INTEGER, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter INTEGER, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, NULL AS FlowCount, Load, SUM(OfferedRate)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS OfferedRate, SUM(ThroughputPercent)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputPercent, SUM(ThroughputMbps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputMbps, SUM(ThroughputFps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputFps, MIN(ThroughputPercent) AS MinThroughputPercent, MAX(ThroughputPercent) AS MaxThroughputPercent, SUM(TotalLatency) AS TotalLatency, 0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency)/SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgLatency, MIN(MinLatency) AS MinLatency, MAX(MaxLatency) AS MaxLatency, SUM(TotalJitter) AS TotalJitter, 0.01 * SUM(TotalJitter) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgJitter, MIN(MinJitter) AS MinJitter, MAX(MaxJitter) AS MaxJitter, SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, SUM(RxFrameCount) AS RxFrameCount, SUM(DroppedFrameCount) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * SUM(DroppedFrameCount) / SUM(TxFrameCount), 0.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) AS OutSeqFrameCount, SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) AS DuplicateFrameCount, SUM(LateFrameCount) AS LateFrameCount, CASE WHEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)>=SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) THEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)-SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) ELSE 0 END AS FloodedFrameCount FROM vsw_pkt_loss
UPDATE vsw_flow_iter_agg SET FlowCount=
(SELECT FlowCount FROM vsw_flow_cfg) WHERE FlowCount IS NULL

SELECT FrameSize AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', FlowCount AS 'Flow Count', Load AS 'Load (%)', ROUND(OfferedRate,3) AS 'Offered Rate (%)', ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent,3) AS 'Avg. Forwarding Rate (%)', ROUND(AvgThroughputMbps,3) AS 'Avg. Forwarding Rate (Mbps)', ROUND(AvgThroughputFps,3) AS 'Avg. Forwarding Rate (fps)', COALESCE(ROUND(AvgLatency, 3), 'NA') AS 'Avg. Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MinLatency, 3), 'NA') AS 'Min. Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MaxLatency, 3), 'NA') AS 'Max. Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(AvgJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Avg. Jitter (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MinJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Min. Jitter (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MaxJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Max. Jitter (us)', TxFrameCount AS 'Tx Frame Count', RxFrameCount AS 'Rx Frame Count', DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', ROUND(DroppedFramePercent, 2) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count', FloodedFrameCount AS 'Flooded Frame Count' FROM vsw_flow_iter_agg ORDER BY rowid DESC LIMIT 1

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_flow_rtchart (FrameSize INTEGER, Flows INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, Throughput FLOAT, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT FrameSize, r.FlowCount AS Flows, ROUND(Load, 3) AS ConfigRate, ROUND(OfferedRate, 3) AS OfferedRate, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent, 3) AS Throughput, DroppedFrameCount, OutSeqFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount FROM vsw_flow_iter_agg AS r JOIN vsw_flow_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize ORDER BY r.rowid DESC LIMIT 1

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_iter_tmp (IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT, CurrVal FLOAT, MaxVal FLOAT, MbpsFactor FLOAT, FpsFactor FLOAT)
DELETE FROM vsw_iter_tmp

SELECT DISTINCT IsConverged, CAST(ConvergedVal AS FLOAT) AS ConvergedVal, CAST(CurrVal AS FLOAT) AS CurrVal, MaxVal, Gc.MbpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS MbpsFactor, Gc.FpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS FpsFactor FROM spirent_methodology_RateIteratorCommand AS Ic JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON Ic.Handle=Rt.SourceHnd JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle, GeneratorConfig AS Gc JOIN Generator AS Gn ON Gn.Handle=Gc.ParentHnd WHERE Tag.Name='RateIter' AND Gn.ParentHnd IN (SELECT DISTINCT ParentHnd FROM StreamBlock)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_flow_iter (FrameSize INTEGER, Flows INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, ConfigRateMbps FLOAT, ConfigRateFps FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, OfferedRateMbps FLOAT, OfferedRateFps FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps FLOAT, TotalLatency INTEGER, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter INTEGER, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER, MaxRate FLOAT, IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, Ag.FlowCount AS Flows, Load AS ConfigRate, ROUND(Load*MbpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateMbps, ROUND(Load*FpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateFps, OfferedRate, ROUND(OfferedRate*MbpsFactor,3) AS OfferedRateMbps, ROUND(OfferedRate*FpsFactor,3) AS OfferedRateFps, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent,3) AS AvgThroughputPercent, ROUND(AvgThroughputMbps,3) AS AvgThroughputMbps, ROUND(AvgThroughputFps,3) AS AvgThroughputFps, TotalLatency, ROUND(AvgLatency,3) AS AvgLatency, ROUND(MinLatency,3) AS MinLatency, ROUND(MaxLatency,3) AS MaxLatency, TotalJitter, ROUND(AvgJitter,3) AS AvgJitter, ROUND(MinJitter,3) AS MinJitter, ROUND(MaxJitter,3) AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, RxFrameCount, DroppedFrameCount, DroppedFramePercent, OutSeqFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount, Ic.MaxVal AS MaxRate, Ic.IsConverged, Ic.ConvergedVal
FROM vsw_flow_iter_agg AS Ag JOIN vsw_flow_cfg AS Cf ON CfgFrameSize=FrameSize AND Ag.FlowCount=Cf.FlowCount, vsw_iter_tmp AS Ic
WHERE Ag.Load=(CASE WHEN Ic.IsConverged THEN Ic.ConvergedVal ELSE Ic.CurrVal END)
